<L>__{interior london club day}
<A>__{roderick having lunch with lord west and the earl of crabs.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{and for a five hundred guinea fee, paid to his city law firm, lord west kindly arranged a meeting with that old scamp and swindler, gustavus adolphus, the thirteenth earl of crabs.}
<C>__{earl of crabs}
<D>__{mr. cosgrove, when i take up a person, he or she is safe. there is no question about them any more. my friends are the best people. i don't mean the most virtuous, or, indeed, the least virtuous, or the cleverest, or the stupidest, or the richest, or the best born, but the "best" in a word, people about whom there is no question. i cannot promise you how long it will take. you can appreciate it is not an easy matter. but any gentlemen with an estate, and ten thousand a year should have a peerage.}
